//@version=6
indicator("Riemannian Dreamer Manifold Engine (RDME)", shorttitle="⟡ RDME [DAFE]", overlay=true, max_bars_back=2000, max_labels_count=500, max_lines_count=500, max_boxes_count=300)
//==============================================================================
// 📚 RIEMANNIAN DREAMER MANIFOLD ENGINE — MATHEMATICAL FRAMEWORK
//==============================================================================
//
// ⟡ RDME models the market as a living Riemannian manifold — a curved geometric
// space whose metric tensor evolves continuously from order flow, volatility,
// momentum, and liquidity pressure. Price travels along geodesics on this
// manifold. Curvature reveals stress (reversal zones) and expansion (sustainable
// trends). A Dreamer world model learns from prediction errors, imagines future
// states via multi-step rollouts, and optimizes policy through Group Relative
// Policy Optimization (GRPO).
//
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// PILLAR 1: RIEMANNIAN METRIC & RICCI CURVATURE
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//
// The market state at each bar is a point on a 3-dimensional manifold with
// coordinates (Pressure, Health, Liquidity). The metric tensor g_ij is
// approximated by the local covariance structure of these coordinates. The
// Ricci scalar curvature R is estimated from second-order dynamics:
//
//   R ≈ ∂²(vol_of_vol) / ∂t² − E[∂(vol_of_vol)/∂t]
//
// Positive R → Market contraction (spherical geometry) → Reversal zones
// Negative R → Market expansion (hyperbolic geometry) → Trend continuation
// R ≈ 0     → Locally flat (Euclidean) → Random walk, low conviction
//
// The Mahalanobis-inspired distance on the manifold measures how far the
// current state is from equilibrium in metric-adjusted coordinates.
//
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// PILLAR 2: ADAPTIVE WAVE TOKEN SYSTEM
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//
// Swing detection uses Hurst-exponent-modulated pivot lengths. The Hurst
// exponent H is estimated via Rescaled Range (R/S) analysis:
//
//   H = log(R/S) / log(n)
//
// H > 0.5 → Trending (persistent) → Pivot contracts to catch emerging waves
// H < 0.5 → Mean-reverting → Pivot expands to filter noise
// H ≈ 0.5 → Random walk → Default pivot
//
// Each completed swing generates a Wave Token carrying 18+ features extracted
// from footprint data: delta efficiency, absorption rate, POC shift, value
// area acceptance, conviction, exhaustion, trap risk, and siege metrics.
//
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// PILLAR 3: SIEGE ENGINE — STRUCTURAL GEOMETRY
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//
// The Siege Engine identifies where price repeatedly tests structural
// levels. It projects dynamic trendlines from consecutive same-direction
// pivot endpoints and scans for bar-level touches within an ATR-scaled
// tolerance band.
//
// For each siege zone, the engine computes:
//   • Hit count and energy decay (diminishing structural strength)
//   • Delta alignment (order flow confirmation at the level)
//   • Break probability P(break) from delta alignment + pressure + decay
//   • Fail probability P(fail) from absorption + opposing flow + decay
//   • Third-push detection (classical exhaustion pattern)
//
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// PILLAR 4: DREAMER RL WORLD MODEL
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//
// The Dreamer is a 3×3 linear neural world model that predicts next-bar
// manifold coordinates from current state:
//
//   ŝ(t+1) = W · s(t) + b
//
// Prediction error drives:
//   • Novelty detection (regime change awareness)
//   • Plasticity modulation (learning rate adaptation)
//   • Imagination rollouts (multi-step forward simulation)
//
// The GRPO system evaluates three action modes (Conservative, Neutral,
// Aggressive) by:
//   1. Running imagination rollouts with Monte Carlo noise
//   2. Computing Sharpe ratios across simulated paths
//   3. Tracking realized P&L of registered trade jobs
//   4. Updating softmax policy via group-relative advantage
//
// The triadic verdict (Pressure + Health + Liquidity consensus) must exceed
// the GRPO-adjusted threshold to generate a signal.
//
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// SIGNAL PHILOSOPHY
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//
// Signals require confluence across all four pillars:
//   1. Manifold curvature supports the direction
//   2. Wave Token structure confirms impulse or correction
//   3. Siege Engine validates structural context
//   4. Dreamer world model projects favorable future value
//
// The system self-adapts across instruments and timeframes through:
//   • Z-score normalization of all features
//   • Hurst-modulated pivot scaling
//   • Novelty-driven plasticity in the world model
//   • GRPO policy that learns which action mode performs best
//
// ⚠️ RISK DISCLAIMER: Despite mathematical sophistication, markets can
// exhibit sudden topology changes (manifold tearing). Always use proper
// risk management, position sizing, and combine with your own analysis.
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// INPUTS
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
string G_CORE = "1. Core Manifold"
int    i_histMax   = input.int(1400, "History Buffer", minval=500, maxval=3000, group=G_CORE, tooltip="Bars of OHLCV + footprint data retained. Larger = deeper wave context but more memory.")
int    i_tokenMax  = input.int(45, "Max Wave Tokens", minval=15, maxval=120, group=G_CORE, tooltip="Maximum completed swing segments stored. Elliott mapper uses last 5 tokens.")
int    i_healthLen = input.int(14, "Health Lookback", minval=6, maxval=40, group=G_CORE, tooltip="Rolling window for directional efficiency calculation.")
int    i_liqFast   = input.int(8, "Liquidity Fast Window", minval=3, maxval=20, group=G_CORE, tooltip="Short-period delta sum for fast liquidity component.")
int    i_liqSlow   = input.int(34, "Liquidity Slow Window", minval=10, maxval=80, group=G_CORE, tooltip="Long-period delta sum for slow liquidity baseline.")
int    i_zLen      = input.int(60, "Z-Score Lookback", minval=20, maxval=200, group=G_CORE, tooltip="Normalization baseline for all Z-scored features.")
int    i_hurstPer  = input.int(80, "Hurst Period", minval=30, maxval=200, group=G_CORE, tooltip="Lookback for R/S Hurst exponent. Drives adaptive pivot scaling.")
int    i_basePivot = input.int(6, "Base Swing Pivot", minval=2, maxval=20, group=G_CORE, tooltip="Starting pivot before Hurst modulation.")
int    i_minPivot  = input.int(3, "Min Pivot", minval=2, maxval=20, group=G_CORE)
int    i_maxPivot  = input.int(14, "Max Pivot", minval=3, maxval=40, group=G_CORE)
string G_FP = "2. Footprint"
int    i_fpTicks   = input.int(100, "Ticks Per Row", minval=1, group=G_FP, tooltip="Tick resolution for footprint data. Falls back to OHLCV proxy if unavailable.")
int    i_fpVA      = input.int(70, "Value Area %", minval=1, maxval=99, group=G_FP)
string G_RL = "3. Dreamer RL Engine"
float  i_baseThr   = input.float(2.1, "Base RL Threshold", step=0.1, group=G_RL, tooltip="Minimum triadic verdict magnitude for trade job registration.")
float  i_wmLR      = input.float(0.009, "World Model LR", step=0.001, group=G_RL, tooltip="How fast the world model adapts. Scaled by plasticity internally.")
int    i_imagDepth = input.int(6, "Imagination Depth", minval=3, maxval=14, group=G_RL, tooltip="Forward simulation steps per rollout.")
int    i_evalH     = input.int(16, "GRPO Eval Horizon", minval=5, maxval=50, group=G_RL, tooltip="Bars before evaluating trade job P&L.")
int    i_grpoEvery = input.int(9, "GRPO Update Frequency", minval=1, maxval=50, group=G_RL)
int    i_maxJobs   = input.int(12, "Max RL Jobs", minval=1, maxval=30, group=G_RL)
string G_VIZ = "4. Visualization"
bool   i_showManifold  = input.bool(true, "⟡ Riemannian Manifold Field", group=G_VIZ)
bool   i_showGeodesics = input.bool(true, "⟡ Geodesic Paths", group=G_VIZ)
bool   i_showTransport = input.bool(true, "⟡ Parallel Transport Particles", group=G_VIZ)
bool   i_showSiege     = input.bool(true, "⟡ Siege Corridors", group=G_VIZ)
bool   i_showDreamer   = input.bool(true, "⟡ Dreamer Projections", group=G_VIZ)
bool   i_showWaveLines = input.bool(true, "⟡ Wave Lines", group=G_VIZ)
bool   i_showLabels    = input.bool(true, "⟡ Signal Labels", group=G_VIZ)
bool   i_showTokenInfo = input.bool(true, "⟡ Token Info Labels", group=G_VIZ)
bool   i_showCurvBg    = input.bool(true, "⟡ Curvature Background", group=G_VIZ)
bool   i_showDashboard = input.bool(true, "📊 Dashboard", group=G_VIZ)
string i_dashPosition  = input.string("top_right", "Dashboard Position", options=["top_left","top_right","bottom_left","bottom_right"], group=G_VIZ)
string i_theme = input.string("CyberPunk", "Theme", options=["CyberPunk","DeepSpace","Institutional"], group=G_VIZ)
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// THEME COLORS
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
color cBull     = i_theme == "CyberPunk" ? #00F5D4 : i_theme == "DeepSpace" ? #22D3EE : #00C853
color cBear     = i_theme == "CyberPunk" ? #FF4D6D : i_theme == "DeepSpace" ? #FB7185 : #D50000
color cWarn     = i_theme == "CyberPunk" ? #FFD166 : i_theme == "DeepSpace" ? #FBBF24 : #FF9100
color cCurv     = i_theme == "CyberPunk" ? #FFD166 : i_theme == "DeepSpace" ? #FBBF24 : #FF9100
color cInfo     = i_theme == "CyberPunk" ? #7C3AED : i_theme == "DeepSpace" ? #60A5FA : #2962FF
color cGold     = #FFD700
color cText     = color.new(color.white, 0)
color cDim      = i_theme == "CyberPunk" ? color.new(#94A3B8, 0) :
                  i_theme == "DeepSpace" ? color.new(#CBD5E1, 0) : color.new(#B0BEC5, 0)
color cBg       = i_theme == "CyberPunk" ? color.new(#080A11, 5) :
                  i_theme == "DeepSpace" ? color.new(#04101C, 5) : color.new(#111111, 5)
color cBorder   = i_theme == "CyberPunk" ? color.new(#2A1B5A, 0) :
                  i_theme == "DeepSpace" ? color.new(#1E3A8A, 0) : color.new(#333333, 0)
color cManifold = #9C4EFF
color cRLOpen   = #E040FB
color cRLEval   = #76FF03
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// CONSTANTS
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
float EPS = 1e-10
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// TYPES
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
type WaveToken
    int   direction
    int   degree
    int   startBar
    int   endBar
    float startPrice
    float endPrice
    int   duration
    float magnitude
    float atrMagnitude
    float angle
    float pressureScore
    float healthScore
    float liquidityScore
    float fpBuyVol
    float fpSellVol
    float fpDeltaVol
    float fpDeltaEff
    float pocShift
    float vaAccept
    float absorptionRate
    float conviction
    float exhaustion
    float trap
    int   siegeHits
    float siegeDecay
    float siegePressure
    float siegeDeltaAlign
    bool  thirdPushFlag
    float siegeBreakProb
    float siegeFailProb
type GrpoAgent
    float total_reward
    int   count
    float advantage
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// HELPERS
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
clamp(float x, float lo, float hi) => math.max(lo, math.min(hi, x))
sgn(float x) => x > 0 ? 1.0 : x < 0 ? -1.0 : 0.0
zscore(float src, int len, float cap) =>
    float avg = nz(ta.sma(src, len), src)
    float sd  = nz(ta.stdev(src, len), 1.0)
    float z   = sd > 0 ? (src - avg) / sd : 0.0
    nz(clamp(z, -cap, cap), 0.0)
prand(float s) =>
    float fract = math.abs(s) * 12.9898 + 78.233
    float r = math.sin(fract) * 43758.5453
    r - math.floor(r)
agree3(float v1, float v2, float v3) =>
    (v1 > 0 and v2 > 0 and v3 > 0) or (v1 < 0 and v2 < 0 and v3 < 0) ? 1.0 : 0.0
align3(float v1, float v2, float v3, float thresh) =>
    (math.abs(v1) > thresh and math.abs(v2) > thresh and math.abs(v3) > thresh) ? 1.0 : 0.0
f_hurstExponent(float src, int length) =>
    float mean = nz(ta.sma(src, length), src)
    float sumDev = 0.0
    float maxDev = 0.0
    float minDev = 0.0
    for i = 0 to length - 1
        float deviation = nz(src[i], src) - mean
        sumDev += deviation
        maxDev := math.max(maxDev, sumDev)
        minDev := math.min(minDev, sumDev)
    float rangeRS = maxDev - minDev
    float stdDev = nz(ta.stdev(src, length), 1.0)
    float rs = stdDev > 0 ? rangeRS / stdDev : 1.0
    float h = rs > 0 ? math.log(rs) / math.log(length) : 0.5
    nz(clamp(h, 0.2, 0.8), 0.5)
f_token_degree(float atrMag, int dur) =>
    atrMag > 10 or dur > 60 ? 3 : atrMag > 5 or dur > 25 ? 2 : 1
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// BASE SERIES
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
float atr14    = nz(ta.atr(14), syminfo.mintick)
float ema21    = nz(ta.ema(close, 21), close)
float ema50    = nz(ta.ema(close, 50), close)
float smaVol20 = nz(ta.sma(volume, 20), volume)
float hurst    = f_hurstExponent(close, i_hurstPer)
int   dynPivot = int(clamp(math.round(i_basePivot * (1.5 - hurst)), i_minPivot, i_maxPivot))
float rng  = math.max(high - low, syminfo.mintick)
float body = math.abs(close - open)
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// RICCI CURVATURE APPROXIMATION
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
float retSeries  = nz(ta.change(close) / close[1], 0.0)
float volOfVol   = ta.stdev(ta.stdev(retSeries, 14), 34)
float volOfVolMA = ta.sma(ta.stdev(retSeries, 14), 34)
float ricciRaw   = nz((volOfVol - volOfVolMA) * 65.0 / atr14, 0.0)
float ricciSmooth = ta.ema(ricciRaw, 8)
bool  isHyperbolic = ricciSmooth < -1.2
bool  isSpherical  = ricciSmooth > 1.2
bool  isFlat       = math.abs(ricciSmooth) <= 1.2
string manifoldRegime = isHyperbolic ? "HYPERBOLIC" : isSpherical ? "SPHERICAL" : "FLAT"
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// FOOTPRINT ENGINE
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
footprint fp = request.footprint(i_fpTicks, i_fpVA)
float fpBuy   = nz(not na(fp) ? fp.buy_volume()  : volume * (close - low) / rng, 0.0)
float fpSell  = nz(not na(fp) ? fp.sell_volume() : volume * (high - close) / rng, 0.0)
float fpDelta = nz(not na(fp) ? fp.delta()       : (fpBuy - fpSell), 0.0)
float fpVah   = na
float fpVal   = na
float fpPocU  = na
float fpPocL  = na
if not na(fp)
    volume_row vahRow = fp.vah()
    volume_row valRow = fp.val()
    volume_row pocRow = fp.poc()
    fpVah  := vahRow.up_price()
    fpVal  := valRow.down_price()
    fpPocU := pocRow.up_price()
    fpPocL := pocRow.down_price()
float fpPocMid     = not na(fpPocU) and not na(fpPocL) ? (fpPocU + fpPocL) / 2.0 : na
float fpTotalVol   = math.max(fpBuy + fpSell, 1.0)
float fpDeltaRatio = nz(fpDelta / fpTotalVol, 0.0)
float fpBuyRatio   = nz(fpBuy / fpTotalVol, 0.5)
float fpImbalance  = math.abs(fpBuyRatio - 0.5) * 2.0
float fpVaWidth    = not na(fpVah) and not na(fpVal) ? nz((fpVah - fpVal) / rng, 1.0) : 1.0
float fpConviction = nz(not na(fp) ? clamp((1.0 - fpVaWidth) * fpImbalance, 0.0, 1.0) :
                     math.abs(close - open) / rng, 0.0)
float fpValueAccept = not na(fp) ? (not na(fpVah) and close > fpVah ? 1.0 :
                      not na(fpVal) and close < fpVal ? -1.0 : 0.0) :
                      (close > ema21 ? 0.5 : -0.5)
float fpAbsorption = ((close > open and fpDelta < 0) or (close < open and fpDelta > 0)) ? 1.0 :
                     (rng < atr14 * 0.5 and volume > smaVol20 ? 0.8 : 0.0)
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// BAR-LEVEL MANIFOLD COORDINATES
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
float uW = high - math.max(open, close)
float lW = math.min(open, close) - low
float uPct = uW / rng * 100.0
float lPct = lW / rng * 100.0
float uZ = zscore(uW, i_zLen, 4.0)
float lZ = zscore(lW, i_zLen, 4.0)
float netPressure = lPct * (lZ > 1 ? 1.5 : 1.0) - uPct * (uZ > 1 ? 1.5 : 1.0)
float pressureBar = nz(clamp(netPressure + fpDeltaRatio * 35.0 +
     (close > open ? 4.0 : close < open ? -4.0 : 0.0), -100.0, 100.0), 0.0)
float moveSum = 0.0
for i = 0 to i_healthLen - 1
    moveSum += nz(math.abs(close[i] - close[i + 1]), 0.0)
float eff = moveSum > 0 ? nz(math.abs(close - close[i_healthLen]) / moveSum, 0.0) : 0.0
float trendDist = atr14 > 0 ? nz((close - ema21) / atr14, 0.0) : 0.0
float healthBar = nz(clamp((eff * 60.0 + trendDist * 18.0 - fpAbsorption * 18.0) *
     sgn(close - ema21), -100.0, 100.0), 0.0)
float fastDelta = nz(math.sum(fpDelta, i_liqFast), 0.0)
float slowDelta = nz(math.sum(fpDelta, i_liqSlow), 0.0)
float fastZ     = zscore(fastDelta, i_zLen, 4.0)
float slowZ     = zscore(slowDelta, i_zLen, 4.0)
float liqDir    = sgn(fastZ + slowZ)
float liqStr    = clamp((math.abs(fastZ) * 0.70 + math.abs(slowZ)) * 20.0, 0.0, 100.0)
float liquidityBar = nz(clamp(liqDir * liqStr, -100.0, 100.0), 0.0)
float triadicVerdict = nz((pressureBar + healthBar + liquidityBar) / 30.0, 0.0)
float harmony = agree3(pressureBar, healthBar, liquidityBar)
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// HISTORY BUFFERS
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
var array<int>   hBars   = array.new_int()
var array<float> hBuy    = array.new_float()
var array<float> hSell   = array.new_float()
var array<float> hDelta  = array.new_float()
var array<float> hPocMid = array.new_float()
var array<float> hVaAcc  = array.new_float()
var array<float> hAbsorb = array.new_float()
var array<float> hConv   = array.new_float()
var array<float> hPress  = array.new_float()
var array<float> hHealth = array.new_float()
var array<float> hLiq    = array.new_float()
var array<float> hHigh   = array.new_float()
var array<float> hLow    = array.new_float()
var array<float> hClose  = array.new_float()
var array<float> hAtr    = array.new_float()
array.push(hBars, bar_index)
array.push(hBuy, fpBuy)
array.push(hSell, fpSell)
array.push(hDelta, fpDelta)
array.push(hPocMid, fpPocMid)
array.push(hVaAcc, fpValueAccept)
array.push(hAbsorb, fpAbsorption)
array.push(hConv, fpConviction)
array.push(hPress, pressureBar)
array.push(hHealth, healthBar)
array.push(hLiq, liquidityBar)
array.push(hHigh, high)
array.push(hLow, low)
array.push(hClose, close)
array.push(hAtr, atr14)
if array.size(hBars) > i_histMax
    array.shift(hBars)
    array.shift(hBuy)
    array.shift(hSell)
    array.shift(hDelta)
    array.shift(hPocMid)
    array.shift(hVaAcc)
    array.shift(hAbsorb)
    array.shift(hConv)
    array.shift(hPress)
    array.shift(hHealth)
    array.shift(hLiq)
    array.shift(hHigh)
    array.shift(hLow)
    array.shift(hClose)
    array.shift(hAtr)
var array<WaveToken> waveTokens = array.new<WaveToken>()
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// SIEGE ENGINE HELPERS
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
f_line_price_at(float p1, int b1, float p2, int b2, int bNow) =>
    float slope = b2 != b1 ? (p2 - p1) / (b2 - b1) : 0.0
    p2 + slope * (bNow - b2)
f_siege_decay(int hits) =>
    hits == 0 ? 1.00 : hits == 1 ? 0.90 : hits == 2 ? 0.75 : hits == 3 ? 0.50 : 0.10
f_scan_siege(int startB, int endB, float aP, int aB, float bP, int bB, bool useLine, float tolAtr, int dir) =>
    int hits = 0
    int deltaAligned = 0
    float pressAgg = 0.0
    float breakV = 0.0
    float failV = 0.0
    bool prevTouched = false
    for i = 0 to array.size(hBars) - 1
        int bi = array.get(hBars, i)
        if bi >= startB and bi <= endB
            float ref = useLine ? f_line_price_at(aP, aB, bP, bB, bi) : bP
            float hi = array.get(hHigh, i)
            float lo = array.get(hLow, i)
            float cl = array.get(hClose, i)
            float at = nz(math.max(array.get(hAtr, i), syminfo.mintick), syminfo.mintick)
            float tol = at * tolAtr
            bool touched = hi >= ref - tol and lo <= ref + tol
            if touched and not prevTouched
                hits += 1
                float pr = array.get(hPress, i)
                float de = array.get(hDelta, i)
                float ab = array.get(hAbsorb, i)
                pressAgg += sgn(pr) * dir
                if sgn(de) == dir
                    deltaAligned += 1
                bool broke = dir == 1 ? cl > ref + tol * 0.15 : cl < ref - tol * 0.15
                bool failed = dir == 1 ? (cl < ref and ab > 0.0) : (cl > ref and ab > 0.0)
                breakV += broke ? 1.0 : 0.0
                failV += failed ? 1.0 : 0.0
            prevTouched := touched
    float decay = f_siege_decay(hits)
    float pressure = hits > 0 ? pressAgg / hits : 0.0
    float dAlign = hits > 0 ? float(deltaAligned) / float(hits) : 0.0
    bool thirdPush = hits == 3
    float h = math.max(float(hits), 1.0)
    float breakProb = hits > 0 ? clamp(0.15 + dAlign * 0.30 + math.max(pressure, 0.0) * 0.20 +
         (1.0 - decay) * 0.10 + (thirdPush ? 0.10 : 0.0) + breakV / h * 0.25, 0.0, 1.0) : 0.0
    float failProb = hits > 0 ? clamp(0.10 + (1.0 - dAlign) * 0.20 + math.max(-pressure, 0.0) * 0.20 +
         (decay < 0.6 ? 0.10 : 0.0) + (thirdPush ? 0.15 : 0.0) + failV / h * 0.25, 0.0, 1.0) : 0.0
    [hits, decay, pressure, dAlign, thirdPush, breakProb, failProb]
f_apply_siege(WaveToken tok) =>
    int sameFound = 0
    float s1P = na, float s2P = na
    int s1B = na, int s2B = na
    if array.size(waveTokens) > 0
        for j = array.size(waveTokens) - 1 to 0
            WaveToken prev = array.get(waveTokens, j)
            if prev.direction == tok.direction
                if sameFound == 0
                    s1P := prev.endPrice
                    s1B := prev.endBar
                else if sameFound == 1
                    s2P := prev.endPrice
                    s2B := prev.endBar
                sameFound += 1
                if sameFound >= 2
                    break
    int sh = 0, float sd = 1.0, float sp = 0.0, float sda = 0.0
    bool st = false, float sb = 0.0, float sf = 0.0
    int dh = 0, float dd = 1.0, float dp = 0.0, float dda = 0.0
    bool dt = false, float db = 0.0, float df = 0.0
    if sameFound >= 1 and not na(s1P)
        [t1,t2,t3,t4,t5,t6,t7] = f_scan_siege(tok.startBar, tok.endBar, s1P, s1B, s1P, s1B, false, 0.20, tok.direction)
        sh := t1, sd := t2, sp := t3, sda := t4, st := t5, sb := t6, sf := t7
    if sameFound >= 2 and not na(s2P) and not na(s1P)
        [u1,u2,u3,u4,u5,u6,u7] = f_scan_siege(tok.startBar, tok.endBar, s2P, s2B, s1P, s1B, true, 0.25, tok.direction)
        dh := u1, dd := u2, dp := u3, dda := u4, dt := u5, db := u6, df := u7
    float div = sameFound >= 2 ? 2.0 : 1.0
    tok.siegeHits := math.max(sh, dh)
    tok.siegeDecay := math.min(sd, dd)
    tok.siegePressure := sameFound > 0 ? (sp + dp) / div : 0.0
    tok.siegeDeltaAlign := sameFound > 0 ? (sda + dda) / div : 0.0
    tok.thirdPushFlag := st or dt
    tok.siegeBreakProb := math.max(sb, db)
    tok.siegeFailProb := math.max(sf, df)
    tok
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// TOKEN BUILDER
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
f_build_token(int startB, float startP, int endB, float endP, int dir) =>
    float buyS = 0.0, float sellS = 0.0, float deltaS = 0.0
    float vaS = 0.0, float absS = 0.0, float convS = 0.0
    float pressS = 0.0, float healthS = 0.0, float liqS = 0.0
    float pocFirst = na, float pocLast = na
    bool gotFirst = false
    int count = 0
    for i = 0 to array.size(hBars) - 1
        int bi = array.get(hBars, i)
        if bi >= startB and bi <= endB
            buyS += array.get(hBuy, i)
            sellS += array.get(hSell, i)
            deltaS += array.get(hDelta, i)
            vaS += array.get(hVaAcc, i)
            absS += array.get(hAbsorb, i)
            convS += array.get(hConv, i)
            pressS += array.get(hPress, i)
            healthS += array.get(hHealth, i)
            liqS += array.get(hLiq, i)
            count += 1
            float p = array.get(hPocMid, i)
            if not na(p)
                if not gotFirst
                    pocFirst := p
                    gotFirst := true
                pocLast := p
    int duration = math.max(endB - startB, 1)
    float magnitude = math.abs(endP - startP)
    float atrMag = nz(magnitude / math.max(atr14, syminfo.mintick), 0.0)
    float angle = nz(math.atan((((endP - startP) / math.max(atr14, syminfo.mintick)) / duration) * 5.0) * 180.0 / math.pi, 0.0)
    float totalVol = math.max(buyS + sellS, 1.0)
    float deltaEff = clamp((dir * deltaS / totalVol) * 2.5, -1.0, 1.0)
    float vaAccept = count > 0 ? dir * vaS / count : 0.0
    float absRate = count > 0 ? absS / count : 0.0
    float conv = count > 0 ? convS / count : 0.0
    float pScore = count > 0 ? dir * pressS / count : 0.0
    float hScore = count > 0 ? dir * healthS / count : 0.0
    float lScore = count > 0 ? dir * liqS / count : 0.0
    float pocShift = not na(pocFirst) and not na(pocLast) ?
         clamp((dir * (pocLast - pocFirst) / math.max(atr14, syminfo.mintick)) * 2.0, -2.0, 2.0) : 0.0
    float exhaustion = clamp((absRate * 0.40) + ((1.0 - clamp(deltaEff, 0.0, 1.0)) * 0.30) +
         ((1.0 - clamp((vaAccept + 1.0) / 2.0, 0.0, 1.0)) * 0.30), 0.0, 1.0)
    float trap = clamp(((deltaEff < 0 ? -deltaEff : 0.0) * 0.50) +
         (absRate * 0.30) + ((vaAccept < 0 ? -vaAccept : 0.0) * 0.20), 0.0, 1.0)
    int degree = f_token_degree(atrMag, duration)
    WaveToken.new(dir, degree, startB, endB, startP, endP, duration, magnitude, atrMag, angle,
         pScore, hScore, lScore, buyS, sellS, deltaS, deltaEff, pocShift, vaAccept,
         absRate, conv, exhaustion, trap, 0, 1.0, 0.0, 0.0, false, 0.0, 0.0)
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// ELLIOTT MAPPER FUNCTIONS
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
f_impulse_score(WaveToken t1, WaveToken t2, WaveToken t3, WaveToken t4, WaveToken t5) =>
    bool bull = t1.direction == 1 and t2.direction == -1 and t3.direction == 1 and t4.direction == -1 and t5.direction == 1
    bool bear = t1.direction == -1 and t2.direction == 1 and t3.direction == -1 and t4.direction == 1 and t5.direction == -1
    float score = 0.0
    float wave3Auth = 0.0
    float termRisk = 0.0
    if bull or bear
        float r2 = t2.magnitude / math.max(t1.magnitude, EPS)
        float r3 = t3.magnitude / math.max(t1.magnitude, EPS)
        float r4 = t4.magnitude / math.max(t3.magnitude, EPS)
        score := 40.0
        score += r2 >= 0.20 and r2 <= 0.95 ? 10.0 : 0.0
        score += r3 >= 0.60 ? 15.0 : 0.0
        score += r4 >= 0.15 and r4 <= 0.85 ? 10.0 : 0.0
        score += t3.magnitude > t1.magnitude * 0.50 ? 10.0 : 0.0
        bool noOverlap = bull ? t4.endPrice >= t1.endPrice * 0.99 : t4.endPrice <= t1.endPrice * 1.01
        score += noOverlap ? 15.0 : 0.0
        wave3Auth := nz(clamp(
             (clamp(t3.fpDeltaEff, 0.0, 1.0) * 0.24) +
             (clamp((t3.vaAccept + 1.0) / 2.0, 0.0, 1.0) * 0.20) +
             (clamp(t3.pocShift / 2.0, 0.0, 1.0) * 0.15) +
             (clamp(t3.conviction, 0.0, 1.0) * 0.12) +
             ((1.0 - clamp(t3.absorptionRate, 0.0, 1.0)) * 0.09) +
             (clamp(t3.siegeBreakProb, 0.0, 1.0) * 0.20), 0.0, 1.0), 0.0)
        termRisk := nz(clamp(
             (t5.exhaustion * 0.28) +
             (t5.trap * 0.20) +
             (clamp(t5.siegeFailProb, 0.0, 1.0) * 0.22) +
             ((t5.thirdPushFlag and t5.siegeHits >= 3) ? 0.12 : 0.0) +
             ((t5.fpDeltaEff < t3.fpDeltaEff * 0.70) ? 0.10 : 0.0) +
             ((t5.pocShift < t3.pocShift * 0.60) ? 0.08 : 0.0), 0.0, 1.0), 0.0)
        score += wave3Auth * 20.0
        score -= termRisk * 15.0
    [nz(clamp(score, 0.0, 100.0), 0.0), wave3Auth, termRisk]
f_correction_score(WaveToken a, WaveToken b, WaveToken c) =>
    bool valid = a.direction == c.direction and b.direction == -a.direction
    float score = 0.0
    if valid
        float rB = b.magnitude / math.max(a.magnitude, EPS)
        float rC = c.magnitude / math.max(a.magnitude, EPS)
        score := 35.0
        score += rB >= 0.20 and rB <= 1.20 ? 15.0 : 0.0
        score += rC >= 0.50 and rC <= 2.00 ? 15.0 : 0.0
        score += clamp((c.conviction * 10.0) + (c.fpDeltaEff * 10.0) + (c.vaAccept * 5.0), -10.0, 20.0)
        score += c.absorptionRate < 0.60 ? 10.0 : 0.0
    nz(clamp(score, 0.0, 100.0), 0.0)
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// SWING ENGINE
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
float ph = ta.pivothigh(high, dynPivot, dynPivot)
float pl = ta.pivotlow(low, dynPivot, dynPivot)
var int   lastSwType  = 0
var int   lastSwBar   = na
var float lastSwPrice = na
if not na(ph)
    int phBar = bar_index - dynPivot
    float phPrice = ph
    if lastSwType == 0
        lastSwType := 1
        lastSwBar := phBar
        lastSwPrice := phPrice
    else if lastSwType == 1
        if phPrice > lastSwPrice
            lastSwBar := phBar
            lastSwPrice := phPrice
    else if lastSwType == -1 and phBar > lastSwBar
        WaveToken upTok = f_build_token(lastSwBar, lastSwPrice, phBar, phPrice, 1)
        upTok := f_apply_siege(upTok)
        array.push(waveTokens, upTok)
        if array.size(waveTokens) > i_tokenMax
            array.shift(waveTokens)
        lastSwType := 1
        lastSwBar := phBar
        lastSwPrice := phPrice
if not na(pl)
    int plBar = bar_index - dynPivot
    float plPrice = pl
    if lastSwType == 0
        lastSwType := -1
        lastSwBar := plBar
        lastSwPrice := plPrice
    else if lastSwType == -1
        if plPrice < lastSwPrice
            lastSwBar := plBar
            lastSwPrice := plPrice
    else if lastSwType == 1 and plBar > lastSwBar
        WaveToken dnTok = f_build_token(lastSwBar, lastSwPrice, plBar, plPrice, -1)
        dnTok := f_apply_siege(dnTok)
        array.push(waveTokens, dnTok)
        if array.size(waveTokens) > i_tokenMax
            array.shift(waveTokens)
        lastSwType := -1
        lastSwBar := plBar
        lastSwPrice := plPrice
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// ELLIOTT MAPPER
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
float bullImpScore = 0.0, float bearImpScore = 0.0
float bullW3Auth = 0.0, float bearW3Auth = 0.0
float bullTermRisk = 0.0, float bearTermRisk = 0.0
float corrScore = 0.0
string primaryStruct = "SCANNING"
float primaryScore = 0.0
float primaryTermRisk = 0.0
int tokCount = array.size(waveTokens)
if tokCount >= 5
    WaveToken t1 = array.get(waveTokens, tokCount - 5)
    WaveToken t2 = array.get(waveTokens, tokCount - 4)
    WaveToken t3 = array.get(waveTokens, tokCount - 3)
    WaveToken t4 = array.get(waveTokens, tokCount - 2)
    WaveToken t5 = array.get(waveTokens, tokCount - 1)
    [iS, iA, iT] = f_impulse_score(t1, t2, t3, t4, t5)
    bool bullPat = t1.direction == 1 and t2.direction == -1 and t3.direction == 1 and t4.direction == -1 and t5.direction == 1
    bool bearPat = t1.direction == -1 and t2.direction == 1 and t3.direction == -1 and t4.direction == 1 and t5.direction == -1
    bullImpScore := bullPat ? iS : 0.0
    bearImpScore := bearPat ? iS : 0.0
    bullW3Auth := bullPat ? iA : 0.0
    bearW3Auth := bearPat ? iA : 0.0
    bullTermRisk := bullPat ? iT : 0.0
    bearTermRisk := bearPat ? iT : 0.0
if tokCount >= 3
    WaveToken a = array.get(waveTokens, tokCount - 3)
    WaveToken b = array.get(waveTokens, tokCount - 2)
    WaveToken c = array.get(waveTokens, tokCount - 1)
    corrScore := f_correction_score(a, b, c)
if bullImpScore >= bearImpScore and bullImpScore >= corrScore and bullImpScore > 55
    primaryStruct := "BULL IMPULSE"
    primaryScore := bullImpScore
    primaryTermRisk := bullTermRisk
else if bearImpScore > bullImpScore and bearImpScore >= corrScore and bearImpScore > 55
    primaryStruct := "BEAR IMPULSE"
    primaryScore := bearImpScore
    primaryTermRisk := bearTermRisk
else if corrScore > 50
    primaryStruct := "CORRECTION"
    primaryScore := corrScore
    primaryTermRisk := 0.0
bool bullActive = primaryStruct == "BULL IMPULSE"
bool bearActive = primaryStruct == "BEAR IMPULSE"
bool corrActive = primaryStruct == "CORRECTION"
bool termWarn   = (bullActive and bullTermRisk > 0.55) or (bearActive and bearTermRisk > 0.55)
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// DREAMER RL WORLD MODEL & GRPO
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
var float w00 = 1.0, var float w01 = 0.0, var float w02 = 0.0
var float w10 = 0.0, var float w11 = 1.0, var float w12 = 0.0
var float w20 = 0.0, var float w21 = 0.0, var float w22 = 1.0
var float b0 = 0.0, var float b1w = 0.0, var float b2w = 0.0
var float ps0 = 0.0, var float ps1 = 0.0, var float ps2 = 0.0
var float predErr = 0.0, var float wmAcc = 0.50
var float novelty = 0.10, var float plasticity = 0.10
var float expFv = 0.0, var float imUnc = 0.0
var int   bestAct = 1, var float actThr = i_baseThr
var float dreamer_dir = 0.0, var float dreamer_conf = 0.0
var array<int>   jb_bar = array.new_int()
var array<int>   jb_act = array.new_int()
var array<int>   jb_dir = array.new_int()
var array<float> jb_px  = array.new_float()
var GrpoAgent ag0 = GrpoAgent.new(0.0, 0, 0.0)
var GrpoAgent ag1 = GrpoAgent.new(0.0, 0, 0.0)
var GrpoAgent ag2 = GrpoAgent.new(0.0, 0, 0.0)
var float pl0 = 0.0, var float pl1 = 0.0, var float pl2 = 0.0
var float pp0 = 0.33, var float pp1 = 0.33, var float pp2 = 0.33
var bool rlJobOpened = false, var bool rlJobEvaled = false
var float rlJobEvalPnl = 0.0
float pLvl = nz(pressureBar) / 100.0
float hLvl = nz(healthBar) / 100.0
float lLvl = nz(liquidityBar) / 100.0
float failRisk = primaryTermRisk
if barstate.isconfirmed
    rlJobOpened := false
    rlJobEvaled := false
    if bar_index > 5
        float predP = b0 + w00 * ps0 + w01 * ps1 + w02 * ps2
        float predH = b1w + w10 * ps0 + w11 * ps1 + w12 * ps2
        float predL = b2w + w20 * ps0 + w21 * ps1 + w22 * ps2
        float e0 = nz(pLvl - predP, 0.0)
        float e1 = nz(hLvl - predH, 0.0)
        float e2 = nz(lLvl - predL, 0.0)
        predErr := nz(math.sqrt((e0*e0 + e1*e1 + e2*e2) / 3.0), 0.0)
        float pErrScaled = predErr * 100.0
        novelty := nz(clamp(pErrScaled / 40.0, 0.0, 1.5), 0.1)
        plasticity := nz(clamp(0.10 + novelty * 0.60, 0.10, 1.00), 0.10)
        float lr = (i_wmLR * plasticity) * 0.0001
        w00 := nz(clamp(w00 + lr * e0 * ps0, -5.0, 5.0), w00)
        w01 := nz(clamp(w01 + lr * e0 * ps1, -5.0, 5.0), w01)
        w02 := nz(clamp(w02 + lr * e0 * ps2, -5.0, 5.0), w02)
        w10 := nz(clamp(w10 + lr * e1 * ps0, -5.0, 5.0), w10)
        w11 := nz(clamp(w11 + lr * e1 * ps1, -5.0, 5.0), w11)
        w12 := nz(clamp(w12 + lr * e1 * ps2, -5.0, 5.0), w12)
        w20 := nz(clamp(w20 + lr * e2 * ps0, -5.0, 5.0), w20)
        w21 := nz(clamp(w21 + lr * e2 * ps1, -5.0, 5.0), w21)
        w22 := nz(clamp(w22 + lr * e2 * ps2, -5.0, 5.0), w22)
        b0  := nz(clamp(b0 + lr * e0 * 50.0, -100.0, 100.0), b0)
        b1w := nz(clamp(b1w + lr * e1 * 50.0, -100.0, 100.0), b1w)
        b2w := nz(clamp(b2w + lr * e2 * 50.0, -100.0, 100.0), b2w)
        float rawAcc = nz(1.0 / (1.0 + pErrScaled / 25.0), 0.5)
        wmAcc := nz(wmAcc * 0.985 + rawAcc * 0.015, 0.5)
        float bestSharpe = -999999.0
        float noiseScale = 0.05 * (1.0 - harmony * 0.35)
        float projS0 = 0.0, float projS1 = 0.0, float projS2 = 0.0
        float av0 = 0.0, float av1 = 0.0, float av2 = 0.0
        float vr0 = 0.0, float vr1 = 0.0, float vr2 = 0.0
        for a = 0 to 2
            float tV = 0.0, float tV2 = 0.0
            float modeBias = a == 0 ? 0.12 : a == 1 ? 0.0 : -0.12
            float fS0 = 0.0, float fS1 = 0.0, float fS2 = 0.0
            for p = 0 to 1
                float ds0 = pLvl * (1.0 + modeBias)
                float ds1 = hLvl * (1.0 + modeBias * 0.80)
                float ds2 = lLvl * (1.0 + modeBias * 0.60)
                float pVal = 0.0
                float disc = 1.0
                for step = 0 to i_imagDepth - 1
                    float seed = bar_index * 1000.0 + a * 100.0 + p * 10.0 + step
                    float ns0 = b0 + w00*ds0 + w01*ds1 + w02*ds2 + prand(seed) * noiseScale
                    float ns1 = b1w + w10*ds0 + w11*ds1 + w12*ds2 + prand(seed+1) * noiseScale
                    float ns2 = b2w + w20*ds0 + w21*ds1 + w22*ds2 + prand(seed+2) * noiseScale
                    float stepHarm = 0.5 * agree3(ns0, ns1, ns2) + 0.5 * align3(ns0, ns1, ns2, 0.70)
                    float latentMean = (ns0 + ns1 + ns2) / 3.0
                    float stepR = latentMean * stepHarm * (1.0 - failRisk * 0.55)
                    pVal += disc * stepR
                    disc *= 0.93
                    ds0 := ns0, ds1 := ns1, ds2 := ns2
                tV += pVal, tV2 += pVal * pVal
                if p == 0
                    fS0 := ds0, fS1 := ds1, fS2 := ds2
            float meanV = tV / 2.0
            float varV = math.abs((tV2 / 2.0) - meanV * meanV)
            float sharpe = meanV / (math.sqrt(varV) + EPS)
            if a == 0
                av0 := meanV, vr0 := varV
            else if a == 1
                av1 := meanV, vr1 := varV
            else
                av2 := meanV, vr2 := varV
            if sharpe > bestSharpe
                bestSharpe := sharpe
                bestAct := a
                projS0 := fS0, projS1 := fS1, projS2 := fS2
        expFv := bestAct == 0 ? av0 : bestAct == 1 ? av1 : av2
        imUnc := math.sqrt((vr0 + vr1 + vr2) / 3.0)
        dreamer_dir := (projS0 + projS1 + projS2) / 3.0
        dreamer_conf := wmAcc * (1.0 - clamp(imUnc * 2.0, 0.0, 0.8))
    int ji = array.size(jb_bar) - 1
    while ji >= 0
        if bar_index - array.get(jb_bar, ji) >= i_evalH
            int jDir = array.get(jb_dir, ji)
            float jPx = array.get(jb_px, ji)
            float jPnl = jDir == 1 ? ((close - jPx) / jPx) * 10000.0 : ((jPx - close) / jPx) * 10000.0
            int jAct = array.get(jb_act, ji)
            if jAct == 0
                ag0.total_reward += jPnl, ag0.count += 1
            else if jAct == 1
                ag1.total_reward += jPnl, ag1.count += 1
            else
                ag2.total_reward += jPnl, ag2.count += 1
            rlJobEvaled := true
            rlJobEvalPnl := jPnl
            array.remove(jb_bar, ji)
            array.remove(jb_act, ji)
            array.remove(jb_dir, ji)
            array.remove(jb_px, ji)
        ji -= 1
    if bar_index % i_grpoEvery == 0
        float ar0 = ag0.count > 0 ? ag0.total_reward / ag0.count : 0.0
        float ar1 = ag1.count > 0 ? ag1.total_reward / ag1.count : 0.0
        float ar2 = ag2.count > 0 ? ag2.total_reward / ag2.count : 0.0
        int gc = 0
        float gs = 0.0
        if ag0.count > 0
            gs += ar0, gc += 1
        if ag1.count > 0
            gs += ar1, gc += 1
        if ag2.count > 0
            gs += ar2, gc += 1
        if gc > 1
            float gm = gs / gc
            float vs = 0.0
            if ag0.count > 0
                vs += math.pow(ar0 - gm, 2)
            if ag1.count > 0
                vs += math.pow(ar1 - gm, 2)
            if ag2.count > 0
                vs += math.pow(ar2 - gm, 2)
            float gstd = math.max(math.sqrt(vs / gc), EPS)
            if ag0.count > 0
                pl0 := pl0 * 0.95 + clamp((ar0 - gm) / gstd, -3.0, 3.0) * 0.10
            if ag1.count > 0
                pl1 := pl1 * 0.95 + clamp((ar1 - gm) / gstd, -3.0, 3.0) * 0.10
            if ag2.count > 0
                pl2 := pl2 * 0.95 + clamp((ar2 - gm) / gstd, -3.0, 3.0) * 0.10
            float mx = math.max(pl0, math.max(pl1, pl2))
            float se0 = math.exp(pl0 - mx)
            float se1 = math.exp(pl1 - mx)
            float se2 = math.exp(pl2 - mx)
            float seS = se0 + se1 + se2
            pp0 := se0 / seS, pp1 := se1 / seS, pp2 := se2 / seS
    float mp0 = pp0 * 0.60 + (bestAct == 0 ? 0.40 : 0.0)
    float mp1 = pp1 * 0.60 + (bestAct == 1 ? 0.40 : 0.0)
    float mp2 = pp2 * 0.60 + (bestAct == 2 ? 0.40 : 0.0)
    float selMult = mp0 >= mp1 and mp0 >= mp2 ? 0.75 : mp1 >= mp2 ? 1.00 : 1.25
    actThr := nz(i_baseThr * selMult, i_baseThr)
    if volume > nz(smaVol20, volume) * 1.05 and array.size(jb_bar) < i_maxJobs
        if math.abs(triadicVerdict) > actThr * 0.75
            array.push(jb_bar, bar_index), array.push(jb_act, 0)
            array.push(jb_dir, triadicVerdict > 0 ? 1 : -1), array.push(jb_px, close)
            rlJobOpened := true
        if math.abs(triadicVerdict) > actThr * 1.00
            array.push(jb_bar, bar_index), array.push(jb_act, 1)
            array.push(jb_dir, triadicVerdict > 0 ? 1 : -1), array.push(jb_px, close)
        if math.abs(triadicVerdict) > actThr * 1.25
            array.push(jb_bar, bar_index), array.push(jb_act, 2)
            array.push(jb_dir, triadicVerdict > 0 ? 1 : -1), array.push(jb_px, close)
    ps0 := pLvl, ps1 := hLvl, ps2 := lLvl
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// SIGNALS
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
bool sigBull = bullActive and primaryScore > 65 and not (bullActive[1] and primaryScore[1] > 65)
bool sigBear = bearActive and primaryScore > 65 and not (bearActive[1] and primaryScore[1] > 65)
bool sigCorr = corrActive and corrScore > 60 and not (corrActive[1] and corrScore[1] > 60)
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// VISUAL ENGINE - DRAWING MANAGEMENT
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
var array<line>  drawLines  = array.new_line()
var array<label> drawLabels = array.new_label()
f_clear() =>
    if array.size(drawLines) > 0
        for i = array.size(drawLines) - 1 to 0
            line.delete(array.get(drawLines, i))
        array.clear(drawLines)
    if array.size(drawLabels) > 0
        for i = array.size(drawLabels) - 1 to 0
            label.delete(array.get(drawLabels, i))
        array.clear(drawLabels)
f_pushLine(line ln) =>
    if not na(ln)
        array.push(drawLines, ln)
        if array.size(drawLines) > 450
            line.delete(array.shift(drawLines))
f_pushLabel(label lb) =>
    if not na(lb)
        array.push(drawLabels, lb)
        if array.size(drawLabels) > 450
            label.delete(array.shift(drawLabels))
float fieldStr = math.min(4.0, math.abs(ricciSmooth) * 0.8)
float fieldOff = atr14 * 0.15 * (1.0 + fieldStr * 0.5)
p1u = plot(i_showManifold ? close + fieldOff * 0.5 : na, color=color.new(cManifold, 75), linewidth=2, title="Manifold Inner+")
p1d = plot(i_showManifold ? close - fieldOff * 0.5 : na, color=color.new(cManifold, 75), linewidth=2, title="Manifold Inner-")
p2u = plot(i_showManifold ? close + fieldOff * 1.0 : na, color=color.new(cManifold, 85), linewidth=1, title="Manifold Mid+")
p2d = plot(i_showManifold ? close - fieldOff * 1.0 : na, color=color.new(cManifold, 85), linewidth=1, title="Manifold Mid-")
p3u = plot(i_showManifold ? close + fieldOff * 1.6 : na, color=color.new(cManifold, 92), linewidth=1, title="Manifold Outer+")
p3d = plot(i_showManifold ? close - fieldOff * 1.6 : na, color=color.new(cManifold, 92), linewidth=1, title="Manifold Outer-")
fill(p1u, p1d, color=i_showManifold ? color.new(cManifold, 92) : na, title="Core Field")
fill(p2u, p1u, color=i_showManifold ? color.new(cManifold, 95) : na, title="Mid Field+")
fill(p1d, p2d, color=i_showManifold ? color.new(cManifold, 95) : na, title="Mid Field-")
fill(p3u, p2u, color=i_showManifold ? color.new(cManifold, 97) : na, title="Outer Field+")
fill(p2d, p3d, color=i_showManifold ? color.new(cManifold, 97) : na, title="Outer Field-")
bgcolor(i_showCurvBg ? (isHyperbolic ? color.new(cBear, 94) : isSpherical ? color.new(cBull, 94) :
     corrActive ? color.new(cInfo, 96) : na) : na, title="Curvature Background")
barcolor(bullActive ? color.new(cBull, 45) : bearActive ? color.new(cBear, 45) : na)
if i_showGeodesics and bar_index % 4 == 0
    line.new(bar_index - 12, ema21[12], bar_index, ema21, color=color.new(cInfo, 55),
         width=1, style=line.style_dotted)
if i_showTransport and math.abs(triadicVerdict) > 1.5
    for i = 0 to 5
        float yOff = math.sin(bar_index * 0.4 + i) * atr14 * 0.18
        color pCol = triadicVerdict > 0 ? cBull : cBear
        label.new(bar_index, close + yOff, "⟡", color=color(na),
             textcolor=color.new(pCol, 25 + i * 8), size=size.tiny, style=label.style_none)
plotshape(sigBull and i_showLabels, title="Bull Signal", style=shape.triangleup, location=location.belowbar, color=color.new(cBull, 0), size=size.tiny)
plotshape(sigBear and i_showLabels, title="Bear Signal", style=shape.triangledown, location=location.abovebar, color=color.new(cBear, 0), size=size.tiny)
plotshape(sigCorr and i_showLabels, title="Correction", style=shape.circle, location=location.abovebar, color=color.new(cInfo, 20), size=size.tiny)
plotshape(rlJobOpened and i_showLabels, title="RL Job", style=shape.diamond, location=location.belowbar, color=color.new(cRLOpen, 20), size=size.tiny)
if barstate.islast
    f_clear()
    if i_showWaveLines and tokCount > 0
        int startIdx = math.max(0, tokCount - 10)
        for i = startIdx to tokCount - 1
            WaveToken t = array.get(waveTokens, i)
            color lc = t.direction == 1 ? color.new(cBull, 15) : color.new(cBear, 15)
            int lw = t.degree == 3 ? 3 : t.degree == 2 ? 2 : 1
            f_pushLine(line.new(t.startBar, t.startPrice, t.endBar, t.endPrice, color=lc, width=lw))
            if i_showTokenInfo
                string txt = (t.direction == 1 ? "UP" : "DN") + " • " +
                     str.tostring(t.atrMagnitude, "0.0") + " ATR\nΔEff " +
                     str.tostring(t.fpDeltaEff, "0.00")
                f_pushLabel(label.new(t.endBar, t.endPrice, txt,
                     style=t.direction == 1 ? label.style_label_down : label.style_label_up,
                     color=color.new(t.direction == 1 ? cBull : cBear, 85),
                     textcolor=cText, size=size.tiny))
    if i_showLabels and bullActive and tokCount >= 5
        string[] nums = array.from("1", "2", "3", "4", "5")
        for j = 0 to 4
            WaveToken t = array.get(waveTokens, tokCount - 5 + j)
            string txt = array.get(nums, j)
            if j == 2
                txt += "\nAUTH " + str.tostring(bullW3Auth * 100.0, "0") + "%"
            if j == 4 and bullTermRisk > 0.35
                txt += "\nTERM " + str.tostring(bullTermRisk * 100.0, "0") + "%"
            f_pushLabel(label.new(t.endBar, t.endPrice, txt,
                 style=t.direction == 1 ? label.style_label_down : label.style_label_up,
                 color=color.new(cGold, 80), textcolor=cGold, size=size.small))
    if i_showLabels and bearActive and tokCount >= 5
        string[] nums2 = array.from("1", "2", "3", "4", "5")
        for j = 0 to 4
            WaveToken t = array.get(waveTokens, tokCount - 5 + j)
            string txt = array.get(nums2, j)
            if j == 2
                txt += "\nAUTH " + str.tostring(bearW3Auth * 100.0, "0") + "%"
            if j == 4 and bearTermRisk > 0.35
                txt += "\nTERM " + str.tostring(bearTermRisk * 100.0, "0") + "%"
            f_pushLabel(label.new(t.endBar, t.endPrice, txt,
                 style=t.direction == 1 ? label.style_label_down : label.style_label_up,
                 color=color.new(cGold, 80), textcolor=cGold, size=size.small))
    if i_showLabels and corrActive and tokCount >= 3
        string[] abc = array.from("A", "B", "C")
        for j = 0 to 2
            WaveToken t = array.get(waveTokens, tokCount - 3 + j)
            f_pushLabel(label.new(t.endBar, t.endPrice, array.get(abc, j),
                 style=t.direction == 1 ? label.style_label_down : label.style_label_up,
                 color=color.new(cInfo, 80), textcolor=cInfo, size=size.small))
    if i_showSiege and tokCount >= 4
        float h1 = na, float h2 = na, float l1 = na, float l2 = na
        int hb1 = na, int hb2 = na, int lb1 = na, int lb2 = na
        int upF = 0, int dnF = 0
        for i = tokCount - 1 to math.max(0, tokCount - 8)
            WaveToken t = array.get(waveTokens, i)
            if t.direction == 1
                if upF == 0
                    h1 := t.endPrice, hb1 := t.endBar
                else if upF == 1
                    h2 := t.endPrice, hb2 := t.endBar
                upF += 1
            else
                if dnF == 0
                    l1 := t.endPrice, lb1 := t.endBar
                else if dnF == 1
                    l2 := t.endPrice, lb2 := t.endBar
                dnF += 1
        float aT = nz(atr14, syminfo.mintick) * 0.25
        if upF >= 2 and not na(h1) and not na(h2) and not na(hb1) and not na(hb2) and hb1 != hb2
            float cU = h1 + ((h1 - h2) / (hb1 - hb2)) * (bar_index - hb1)
            f_pushLine(line.new(hb2, h2, bar_index, cU, color=color.new(cCurv, 60), style=line.style_dashed, width=1))
            f_pushLine(line.new(hb2, h2+aT, bar_index, cU+aT, color=color.new(cCurv, 75), style=line.style_dotted))
            f_pushLine(line.new(hb2, h2-aT, bar_index, cU-aT, color=color.new(cCurv, 75), style=line.style_dotted))
        if dnF >= 2 and not na(l1) and not na(l2) and not na(lb1) and not na(lb2) and lb1 != lb2
            float cD = l1 + ((l1 - l2) / (lb1 - lb2)) * (bar_index - lb1)
            f_pushLine(line.new(lb2, l2, bar_index, cD, color=color.new(cInfo, 60), style=line.style_dashed, width=1))
            f_pushLine(line.new(lb2, l2+aT, bar_index, cD+aT, color=color.new(cInfo, 75), style=line.style_dotted))
            f_pushLine(line.new(lb2, l2-aT, bar_index, cD-aT, color=color.new(cInfo, 75), style=line.style_dotted))
    if i_showDreamer and math.abs(dreamer_dir) > 0.01 and not na(atr14) and atr14 > 0
        float projPrice = close + dreamer_dir * atr14 * i_imagDepth * 0.30
        int projEnd = bar_index + i_imagDepth
        color projCol = dreamer_dir > 0 ? color.new(cBull, 40) : color.new(cBear, 40)
        int projW = dreamer_conf > 0.55 ? 3 : dreamer_conf > 0.35 ? 2 : 1
        f_pushLine(line.new(bar_index, close, projEnd, projPrice, color=projCol,
             style=line.style_arrow_right, width=projW))
        float cone = atr14 * (1.0 - dreamer_conf) * i_imagDepth * 0.15
        if cone > 0
            f_pushLine(line.new(bar_index, close, projEnd, projPrice + cone,
                 color=color.new(projCol, 75), style=line.style_dotted))
            f_pushLine(line.new(bar_index, close, projEnd, projPrice - cone,
                 color=color.new(projCol, 75), style=line.style_dotted))
        string projTxt = "DREAM " + (dreamer_dir > 0 ? "▲" : "▼") +
             "\nConf " + str.tostring(dreamer_conf * 100, "0") + "%" +
             "\n" + (bestAct == 0 ? "CON" : bestAct == 1 ? "NEU" : "AGG")
        f_pushLabel(label.new(projEnd, projPrice, projTxt,
             style=label.style_label_left, color=color.new(projCol, 80),
             textcolor=cText, size=size.tiny))
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// DASHBOARD
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
dashPos = i_dashPosition == "top_left" ? position.top_left : i_dashPosition == "bottom_left" ? position.bottom_left : i_dashPosition == "bottom_right" ? position.bottom_right : position.top_right
var table tb = na
if barstate.islast
    if not na(tb)
        table.delete(tb)
    tb := table.new(dashPos, 4, 36, bgcolor=cBg, border_color=cBorder, border_width=1, frame_color=cBorder, frame_width=2)
f_sec(table t, int row, int col, string title, color c) =>
    table.cell(t, col, row, title, text_color=c, text_size=size.tiny, bgcolor=color.new(c, 88))
    table.cell(t, col+1, row, "", text_color=c, text_size=size.tiny, bgcolor=color.new(c, 88))
    table.merge_cells(t, col, row, col+1, row)
f_pair(table t, int row, int col, string k, string v, color vc) =>
    table.cell(t, col, row, k, text_color=cDim, text_size=size.tiny, text_halign=text.align_left, bgcolor=color.new(cBg, 0))
    table.cell(t, col+1, row, v, text_color=vc, text_size=size.tiny, text_halign=text.align_right, bgcolor=color.new(cBg, 0))
if barstate.islast and i_showDashboard and not na(tb)
    table.cell(tb, 0, 0, "⟡ RIEMANNIAN DREAMER MANIFOLD                    DAFE",
         text_color=cText, text_size=size.small, text_halign=text.align_center,
         bgcolor=color.new(cManifold, 85))
    table.merge_cells(tb, 0, 0, 3, 0)
    int l = 1
    f_sec(tb, l, 0, "⟡ MANIFOLD FIELD", cManifold)
    l += 1
    f_pair(tb, l, 0, "Primary", primaryStruct, bullActive ? cBull : bearActive ? cBear : corrActive ? cInfo : cDim)
    l += 1
    f_pair(tb, l, 0, "Score", str.tostring(primaryScore, "0.0"), primaryScore > 65 ? cGold : primaryScore > 50 ? cCurv : cDim)
    l += 1
    f_pair(tb, l, 0, "Term Risk", str.tostring(primaryTermRisk * 100.0, "0.0") + "%", primaryTermRisk > 0.55 ? cBear : primaryTermRisk > 0.35 ? cCurv : cBull)
    l += 1
    f_pair(tb, l, 0, "Correction", str.tostring(corrScore, "0.0"), corrActive ? cInfo : cDim)
    l += 1
    f_pair(tb, l, 0, "Pivot / Hurst", str.tostring(dynPivot) + " / " + str.tostring(hurst, "0.00"), hurst > 0.55 ? cBull : hurst < 0.45 ? cCurv : cDim)
    l += 1
    f_pair(tb, l, 0, "Ricci", str.tostring(ricciSmooth, "0.00"),
         isHyperbolic ? cBear : isSpherical ? cBull : cDim)
    l += 1
    f_pair(tb, l, 0, "Regime", manifoldRegime,
         isHyperbolic ? cBear : isSpherical ? cBull : cDim)
    l += 1
    f_pair(tb, l, 0, "Triadic", str.tostring(triadicVerdict, "0.00"),
         triadicVerdict > 0 ? cBull : triadicVerdict < 0 ? cBear : cDim)
    l += 1
    f_pair(tb, l, 0, "Tokens", str.tostring(tokCount) + " / " + str.tostring(i_tokenMax),
         tokCount >= 5 ? cBull : cCurv)
    l += 1
    f_sec(tb, l, 0, "📊 FOOTPRINT", cCurv)
    l += 1
    f_pair(tb, l, 0, "Status", not na(fp) ? "ACTIVE" : "PROXY", not na(fp) ? cBull : cDim)
    l += 1
    f_pair(tb, l, 0, "Delta", str.tostring(fpDelta, "0"), fpDelta > 0 ? cBull : fpDelta < 0 ? cBear : cDim)
    l += 1
    f_pair(tb, l, 0, "Buy Vol %", str.tostring(fpBuyRatio * 100.0, "0.0") + "%",
         fpBuyRatio > 0.55 ? cBull : fpBuyRatio < 0.45 ? cBear : cDim)
    l += 1
    f_pair(tb, l, 0, "POC Bias", na(fpPocMid) ? "NA" :
         close > fpPocMid ? "ABOVE" : close < fpPocMid ? "BELOW" : "AT",
         na(fpPocMid) ? cDim : close > fpPocMid ? cBull : cBear)
    l += 1
    int r = 1
    f_sec(tb, r, 2, "🤖 RL AGENT", cGold)
    r += 1
    f_pair(tb, r, 2, "WM Acc", str.tostring(wmAcc * 100.0, "0.0") + "%", wmAcc > 0.50 ? cBull : cCurv)
    r += 1
    f_pair(tb, r, 2, "Plasticity", str.tostring(plasticity, "0.00"), plasticity > 0.50 ? cCurv : cText)
    r += 1
    f_pair(tb, r, 2, "Exp FV", str.tostring(expFv, "0.00"),
         expFv > 0 ? cBull : expFv < 0 ? cBear : cDim)
    r += 1
    f_pair(tb, r, 2, "Threshold", str.tostring(actThr, "0.00"), cText)
    r += 1
    f_pair(tb, r, 2, "Policy C/N/A", str.tostring(pp0*100,"0") + "/" +
         str.tostring(pp1*100,"0") + "/" + str.tostring(pp2*100,"0"), cText)
    r += 1
    f_pair(tb, r, 2, "Best Action", bestAct == 0 ? "CONSERV" : bestAct == 1 ? "NEUTRAL" : "AGGRESS", bestAct == 0 ? cBull : bestAct == 1 ? cGold : cCurv)
    r += 1
    f_pair(tb, r, 2, "Active Jobs", str.tostring(array.size(jb_bar)) + " / " + str.tostring(i_maxJobs), array.size(jb_bar) >= i_maxJobs ? cCurv : cDim)
    r += 1
    f_pair(tb, r, 2, "Dreamer Dir", str.tostring(dreamer_dir, "0.00") + " @ " +
         str.tostring(dreamer_conf * 100, "0") + "%",
         dreamer_dir > 0 ? cBull : dreamer_dir < 0 ? cBear : cDim)
    r += 1
    f_sec(tb, r, 2, "🧠 TOKEN STATE", cGold)
    r += 1
    if tokCount > 0
        WaveToken lastTok = array.get(waveTokens, tokCount - 1)
        f_pair(tb, r, 2, "Last Token", (lastTok.direction == 1 ? "UP" : "DN") + " " +
             str.tostring(lastTok.atrMagnitude, "0.0") + " ATR",
             lastTok.direction == 1 ? cBull : cBear)
        r += 1
        f_pair(tb, r, 2, "ΔEff", str.tostring(lastTok.fpDeltaEff, "0.00"),
             lastTok.fpDeltaEff > 0 ? cBull : lastTok.fpDeltaEff < 0 ? cBear : cDim)
        r += 1
        f_pair(tb, r, 2, "POC Shift", str.tostring(lastTok.pocShift, "0.00"),
             lastTok.pocShift > 0 ? cBull : lastTok.pocShift < 0 ? cBear : cDim)
        r += 1
        f_pair(tb, r, 2, "Absorption", str.tostring(lastTok.absorptionRate * 100.0, "0.0") + "%", lastTok.absorptionRate > 0.45 ? cCurv : cBull)
        r += 1
        f_pair(tb, r, 2, "Exhaustion", str.tostring(lastTok.exhaustion * 100.0, "0.0") + "%", lastTok.exhaustion > 0.55 ? cBear : lastTok.exhaustion > 0.35 ? cCurv : cBull)
        r += 1
        f_pair(tb, r, 2, "Siege B/F", str.tostring(lastTok.siegeBreakProb * 100.0, "0") + "% / " +
             str.tostring(lastTok.siegeFailProb * 100.0, "0") + "%",
             lastTok.siegeBreakProb > lastTok.siegeFailProb ? cBull : cBear)
        r += 1
    else
        f_pair(tb, r, 2, "Last Token", "NONE", cDim)
        r += 1
    f_sec(tb, r, 2, "📐 WAVE GRAMMAR", cGold)
    r += 1
    f_pair(tb, r, 2, "Bull Impulse", str.tostring(bullImpScore, "0.0"),
         bullImpScore > 60 ? cBull : cDim)
    r += 1
    f_pair(tb, r, 2, "Bear Impulse", str.tostring(bearImpScore, "0.0"),
         bearImpScore > 60 ? cBear : cDim)
    r += 1
    f_pair(tb, r, 2, "W3 Auth B/S", str.tostring(bullW3Auth * 100.0, "0") + "% / " +
         str.tostring(bearW3Auth * 100.0, "0") + "%", cText)
    r += 1
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// ALERTS
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
alertcondition(sigBull, "RDME Bull Impulse", "⟡ RDME Bull Impulse Signal")
alertcondition(sigBear, "RDME Bear Impulse", "⟡ RDME Bear Impulse Signal")
alertcondition(sigCorr, "RDME Correction", "⟡ RDME Correction Complete")
alertcondition(termWarn, "RDME Terminal Warning", "⟡ RDME Terminal Risk Rising")
alertcondition(rlJobOpened, "RDME RL Job", "⟡ RDME RL Agent registered job")
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// DATA WINDOW DIAGNOSTICS
//═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
plot(primaryScore, "Primary Score", color.new(color.white, 100), display=display.data_window)
plot(bullImpScore, "Bull Impulse", color.new(color.white, 100), display=display.data_window)
plot(bearImpScore, "Bear Impulse", color.new(color.white, 100), display=display.data_window)
plot(corrScore, "Correction", color.new(color.white, 100), display=display.data_window)
plot(ricciSmooth, "Ricci Curvature", color.new(color.white, 100), display=display.data_window)
plot(hurst, "Hurst", color.new(color.white, 100), display=display.data_window)
plot(triadicVerdict, "Triadic Verdict", color.new(color.white, 100), display=display.data_window)
plot(pressureBar, "Pressure", color.new(color.white, 100), display=display.data_window)
plot(healthBar, "Health", color.new(color.white, 100), display=display.data_window)
plot(liquidityBar, "Liquidity", color.new(color.white, 100), display=display.data_window)
plot(wmAcc, "WM Accuracy", color.new(color.white, 100), display=display.data_window)
plot(expFv, "Expected FV", color.new(color.white, 100), display=display.data_window)
plot(dreamer_dir, "Dreamer Dir", color.new(color.white, 100), display=display.data_window)
plot(dreamer_conf, "Dreamer Conf", color.new(color.white, 100), display=display.data_window)
plot(float(tokCount), "Token Count", color.new(color.white, 100), display=display.data_window)
plot(float(dynPivot), "Dynamic Pivot", color.new(color.white, 100), display=display.data_window)
plot(float(array.size(jb_bar)), "Active Jobs", color.new(color.white, 100), display=display.data_window)